      "type": "shield",
      "description": "<p><strong>Exoskeleton and Mecha frames only.</strong></p><hr /><p>While driving this <strong>personal vehicle</strong>, you gain a +2 bonus to Defense and a +2 bonus to Magic Defense. Additionally, this weapon module <strong>does not</strong> count as a “weapon”: instead, it counts as an equipped <strong>shield</strong>. This module <strong>cannot</strong> be equipped in your <strong>main hand slot</strong>, unless you have acquired the @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.aPQXTQegswRisA1R]{Dual Shieldbearer} Skill. If you have, your @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.2LyT2btVVPDPYY4h]{Twin Shields} deal 2 extra damage (this is cumulative if you have two <strong>Shield modules</strong> enabled at the same time).</p>",
